---
// IMPORTS CONSTANTS
import { CDN_LINK, IMAGE_QUALITY } from "../../constants/image"

// IMPORTS ASTRO ATOMS
import HeadingTwo from "../../atoms/heading/two/Vanilla.astro"
import Paragraph from "../../atoms/paragraph/Vanilla.astro"

// IMPORTS ASTRO LAYOUTS
import Container from "../../layouts/Container.astro"
---
<Container>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-20 py-32">
        <div class="col-span-3 flex items-center">
            <div class="w-full aspect-[3/2] bg-zinc-200">
                <img
                    src=""
                    alt=""
                    class="w-full h-full"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-6 col-span-2">
            <HeadingTwo>What if I’m not 100% sure what I want?</HeadingTwo>
            <div class="space-y-1">
                <div class="h-[2px] w-14 bg-om_red"></div>
                <div class="h-[2px] w-14 bg-om_red"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="font-proxima_nova text-2xl">That’s understandable. Priorities shift during the process.</p>
            <Paragraph>What you need from your web design company changes throughout the process and over time. We know this from our direct experience with over 1000 projects and clients.

                While your goals are ever-present, your focus will shift as the web design process helps you redefine objectives. That’s to be expected. We adapt.</Paragraph>
        </div>
    </div>
</Container>
